      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p>Which of the following alkyl halides would you expect to undergo Friedel–Crafts reaction with rearrangement and which without? Explain.</p>\n<p><b>(a)</b> CH<sub>3</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>Cl <b>(b)</b> CH<sub>3</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CH(Cl)CH<sub>3</sub> <b>(c)</b> CH<sub>3</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>Cl <b>(d)</b> (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>CCH<sub>2</sub>Cl\n<br><b>(e)</b> Chlorocyclohexane</p>",
